#, fuzzy
msgid "You can get the full changelog of https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.0.CR1[3.30.0.CR1], https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.0[3.30.0], and https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.1[3.30.1] on GitHub."
msgstr "O senhor pode obter o registro completo de alterações das versões link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.0.CR1[3.30.0.CR1] , link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.0[3.30.0] e link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.30.1[3.30.1] no GitHub."

